- 在VS中，右键ui文件，点击compile，编译一下

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

- 右键Header File，选择&quot;Add-&gt;New Item...&quot;

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

- 新建一个.h文件

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

- 内容如下

```ruby
#ifndef EDIT_WINDOW_DIALOG_H
#define EDIT_WINDOW_DIALOG_H
#include "ui_editwindowdialog.h"
#include <QtGui>
#include <QWidget>
#include <QDialog>
class EditWindowPlugin;
class EditWindowDialog : public QDockWidget{
	Q_OBJECT
public:
	EditWindowDialog(QWidget *parent,EditWindowPlugin *_edit);
	~EditWindowDialog(){};
	Ui::Form ui;
	virtual void closeEvent ( QCloseEvent * event );
private:
	EditWindowPlugin *edit;
signals:
	void closing();
	void updateMeshSetVisibilities();
};
#endif
```

右键Source File，选择&quot;Add-&gt;New Item...&quot;再新建一个EditWindowDialog.cpp文件

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

内容如下：

```ruby
#include "EditWindowDialog.h"
#include <GL/glew.h>
#include <QtGui>
#include <meshlab/glarea.h>
void EditWindowDialog::closeEvent ( QCloseEvent * /*event*/ )
{
	emit closing();
}
EditWindowDialog::EditWindowDialog(QWidget *parent,EditWindowPlugin *_edit)
{
	ui.setupUi(this);
	this->setFeatures(QDockWidget::AllDockWidgetFeatures);
	this->setAllowedAreas(Qt::LeftDockWidgetArea);
	QPoint p=parent->mapToGlobal(QPoint(0,0));
	this->setFloating(true);
	this->edit = _edit;
}
```
